      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAZORBACK RORY (8) settled well back early on debut and always towards the tail to finish sixth (23.79) at this track over 400m. Should be further improved and rates on top this time. ZATARA FIRE (4) is still a maiden after 13 runs but rarely out of the placings, the latest filling a minor again when second at this track. Has hit the frame at the last three starts. Comes through a solid form race last start. Racing well and deserves a win. BROADSIDE BALLAD (7) improved his time on first attempt here at the trip with a 0.8 lengths third in 17.55 latest. Has the ability and can measure up. KING POTATO (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
